name: As my colorful dreams paint my sorrow
description: Diela, a colorful fantasy world, was sharing her sadness with her friends. *My thanks to @dielamaharanie and @jjjjjjjjjjohn for making this nft possible. @dielamaharanie's #dielascoloringpage collab meet @jjjjjjjjjjohn's window tribute. I colored OBJKT#113266 "coloring page 01" with colored pencils and some markers. I just added a few minor details to the Diela's original drawing.
